# Admin Panel Audit & Implementation Guide

This is a comprehensive audit of `apps/admin-dashboard/`. Use this as your source of truth when working on the admin panel.

## Project Structure

```
apps/admin-dashboard/src/
├── api.ts                    # All API functions (currently ~77, backend has ~213 endpoints)
├── App.tsx                   # Router with all routes
├── main.tsx                  # Entry point
├── index.css                 # Global styles (NO mobile breakpoints currently)
├── components/
│   ├── Layout.tsx            # Sidebar navigation + top bar + route outlet
│   ├── SharedUI.tsx          # Shared UI primitives (PageHeader, StatCard, etc.)
│   ├── ErrorBoundary.tsx     # Error boundary wrapper
│   └── ui/                   # Reusable components (Badge, Button, Card, Modal, etc.)
├── hooks/
│   ├── usePageTitle.ts
│   └── usePermissions.ts
└── pages/                    # 22 page components (one per route)
```

Backend API routes are in:
- `backend/routes/api.php` — Main API routes (~160+ endpoints)
- `backend/routes/api_finance.php` — Finance routes (invoices, expenses, P&L, etc.)

